
### Login to get token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

### List Plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/plans HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Get Plan by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/plans/{{planID}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Create Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/plans HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

{
  "name": "Pro Plan",
  "description": "Professional plan for power users",
  "price": 29.99,
  "interval": "monthly",
